WEBVTT

1
00:01:03.146 --> 00:01:04.356
What the hell is that?

2
00:01:11.446 --> 00:01:13.490
What's going on? Oh my god.

3
00:01:14.700 --> 00:01:16.326
Port side engine's on fire.

4
