12
00:04:12.961 --> 00:04:14.421
Go. go. go. go. go.

13
00:04:14.504 --> 00:04:17.507
Korsky. Hoyte.
Gardner. Castle. move.

14
00:04:17.591 --> 00:04:18.550
Get to work.

15
00:04:18.633 --> 00:04:20.761
Simms. rear!

16
00:04:22.512 --> 00:04:25.682
Everyone else.
keep your goddamn ears open.

17
00:04:25.766 --> 00:04:27.809
Vehicle. six o'clock!

18
00:04:39.780 --> 00:04:40.822
Easy. Sergeant.

19
00:04:43.366 --> 00:04:44.451
Fuck.

20
00:04:46.411 --> 00:04:49.539
Son of a fucking...
Major Johnson.

21
00:04:50.665 --> 00:04:52.167
What a surprise.

22
00:04:53.001 --> 00:04:56.087
I was told you were
running operations

23
00:04:56.129 --> 00:04:59.466
from a chateau
outside of Reims. sir.

24
00:04:59.549 --> 00:05:01.301
Yeah. well. I guess
I got a little tired

25
