and foie gras.

26
00:05:05.639 --> 00:05:09.351
Well. I just hope you didn't
make the drive in vain. sir.

27
00:05:11.061 --> 00:05:13.438
You know. Sergeant.
a conductor needs to just

28
00:05:13.522 --> 00:05:15.732
