Yeah. but if I'm in jail.

45
00:06:19.588 --> 00:06:22.090
who's gonna do your
dirty work. huh?

46
00:06:22.173 --> 00:06:24.175
It's nice to see
you haven't changed.

47
00:06:25.802 --> 00:06:27.095
It's great catching up. Sergeant.

48
00:06:27.178 --> 00:06:28.638
It's always such a
pleasure to see you.

49
00:06:30.140 --> 00:06:33.476
Well. but as you know.
time is of the essence.

50
00:06:45.238 --> 00:06:46.489
Come here.

51
00:06:52.579 --> 00:06:56.499
Don't just stand around.
we're working. man.

52
00:06:56.583 --> 00:06:58.001
You ever whacked any Jerries?

53
00:07:00.086 --> 00:07:03.006
