of whacked. sir.

54
00:07:03.089 --> 00:07:05.842
Christ. just keeps
getting better and better.

55
00:07:08.511 --> 00:07:10.722
All right. listen up. boys.

56
00:07:10.805 --> 00:07:11.973
We're gonna find that wreckage

57
00:07:12.057 --> 00:07:13.767
