58
00:07:13.850 --> 00:07:16.561
and we're gonna let this
guy sift through the rest.

59
00:07:19.272 --> 00:07:20.982
Let's move out!

60
00:07:21.066 --> 00:07:22.442
Get moving. come on. hey!

61
00:07:33.119 --> 00:07:36.081
You know. when we
were at Marseilles.

62
00:07:36.164 --> 00:07:38.708
I pulled Brewer
from a burning APC.

63
