a crater where they'd been.

69
00:07:58.103 --> 00:08:01.773
Brewer still despises me for it.

70
00:08:01.856 --> 00:08:04.025
He'd rather die a
thousand deaths himself

71
00:08:04.109 --> 00:08:06.778
than lose a single damn soldier.

72
00:08:09.322 --> 00:08:10.824
That's the kind of man he is.

73
00:08:12.617 --> 00:08:15.829
And I'll tell you what. I sure
wish we had more like him.

74
00:08:15.912 --> 00:08:18.748
All right. waterproof your
gear. we're taking the scenic route.

75
00:08:18.832 --> 00:08:20.208
Yes. Sarge.

76
00:08:20.291 --> 00:08:22.669
All right. wait. fuck. just wait.

77
