288
00:31:08.075 --> 00:31:09.868
Let's move.

289
00:31:28.053 --> 00:31:29.888
Friar. north perimeter.

290
00:31:29.971 --> 00:31:32.099
Rucker south. rest of
you sweep for survivors.

